Libraries methods used

1. App
   a1. npm i react-router-dom
   a2. https://reactrouter.com/en/main/start/tutorial
   a3. use of reduce() to display the total quantity in the cart
2. header
   2a. neomorphism
   2b. create a state to chage the background color and do some animation to hide and show the header
3. Home Screen
   3a. use the <Link /> instead of <a /> from rrd
4. Product Screen
5. server.js
   5a. npm i nodemon --save-dev - use to monitor the backend server and doens't require to stop and restart the server in every changes. --save-dev means this is to be use only during development and not in production mode

   5b. npm i axios

6. npm i use-reducer-logger --force >>> not used. brings trouble to the app

7. https://mui.com/ - material UI started to use to improve the UI of the Product.jsx
8. npm i react-helmet-async
9. material ui icons >>> npm install @mui/icons-material @mui/material @emotion/styled @emotion/react
10. npm i bcryptjs
11. npm i express-async-handler
12. npm i jsonwebtoken in be
